# Gold provider bakeoff — generated artifacts.
#
# These files are produced by `scripts/python/provider_bakeoff.py` and
# `scripts/python/provider_scorecard.py`. They are normally uploaded as
# workflow artifacts, NOT committed. The bakeoff workflow only commits
# them when the operator explicitly sets `commit_results=true`; in that
# case use `git add -f data/provider_bakeoff_log.jsonl
# data/provider_scorecard.json` to bypass this ignore.
#
# Important: do NOT add the curated state files
# `data/gold_price.json`, `data/last_gold_price.json`,
# `data/provider_state.json`, or `data/last_tweet_state.json` here —
# those are tracked source-of-truth files.
data/provider_bakeoff_log.jsonl
data/provider_scorecard.json
data/provider_test_results.json
data/provider_bakeoff_*.jsonl
data/provider_scorecard_*.json
